<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bicycle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> DidYouKnow.cd. <a href="http://www.didyouknow.cd/bicycles.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.didyouknow.cd/bicycles.htm" rel="nofollow">There are about a billion or more bicycles in the world.</a> Retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-07-30"><a href="/wiki/July_30" title="July 30">30 July</a> <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span>.</li>
